me were going to have dinner.

20:43.950 --> 20:46.085
I thought this was way
better, don't you think?

20:46.119 --> 20:48.921
I really had no idea anything was
going on with you and Madison and Lauren

20:48.955 --> 20:49.855
because someone didn't tell me.

20:49.889 --> 20:51.190
Someone waited to text me during dinner.

20:51.958 --> 20:54.793
I didn't know what else to do.

20:54.828 --> 20:56.095
Nice poker face, Dad.

20:56.129 --> 20:57.997
(SIGHS)

20:58.031 --> 20:59.999
She slept with him?
What happened to Jack?

21:00.033 --> 21:03.002
(SCOFFS) I don't know.

21:03.036 --> 21:07.106
Jack's always been in love with Grace.
