to get over it, Dad.

22:28.054 --> 22:30.956
My best friend slept with my
other best friend's boyfriend.

22:30.990 --> 22:32.991
She's not my best friend anymore.

22:33.026 --> 22:35.794
Are you really in any
place to judge anyone?

22:35.829 --> 22:36.995
